CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 9, 1964, pg. 5 reads: "Honors - Shown presenting a framed copy of Courier Artist A.S. (Sam) Milai's portrait of Msgr. Raymond A. Must to the clergyamn [sic], left is Msgr. Joseph Schultz. The Rev. John N. LaBauve, guest speaker, observes. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three priests, left to right: Msgr. Raymond A. Must, Rev. John N. LaBauve, and Msgr. Joseph Schultz, holding end of framed illustration of Father Raymond A. Must, for testimonial dinner, Loendi Club
